    "messageBody": "<div id=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927\">\n<html><head>\n \n\n\n</head> \n \n<div><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\">I read \nthe fine manual and here&#39;s what I came up with that works. Please advise if this \ncould be better...</span></font></div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\"><span\n class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\"></span></font>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PrintStream oldOut = \nSystem.out;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ByteArrayOutputStream \nbaos = new \nByteArrayOutputStream(256);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nPrintStream ps = new \nPrintStream(baos);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nSystem.setOut(ps);</font></div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\"></font>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><font\n size=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span\n class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\">&lt;call to program that generates \noutput&gt;</span></font></font></font></div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><font size=\"2\"><span\n class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\"></span></font></font></font>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; String s = \nbaos.toString();<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nassertEquals(&quot;<span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\">&lt;some string that I \nexpect&gt;</span>&quot;, s);<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nSystem.setOut(oldOut);<br></font></div>\n<div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\">Thanks \nfor the pointers guys. :-)</font></span></div>\n<div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\"></font></span>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927690312017-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\">Simon</font></span></div>\n<blockquote><span title=\"qreply\"> <blockquote\n style=\"PADDING-LEFT:5px;MARGIN-LEFT:5px;BORDER-LEFT:#0000ff 2px solid;\">\n  <div class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927OutlookMessageHeader\" dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"\n size=\"2\">-----Original Message-----<br><b>From:</b> Chappell, Simon P \n  <br><b>Sent:</b> Wednesday, November 28, 2001 10:56 AM<br><b>To:</b> \n  junit@yahoogroups.com<br><b>Subject:</b> RE: [junit] Capturing the standard \n  out of a program that I&#39;m testing<br><br></font></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927043495516-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\">The \n  in-memory part sounds good. Do you have a code-fragment that you could share? \n  :-)</font></span></div>\n  <blockquote\n style=\"PADDING-LEFT:5px;MARGIN-LEFT:5px;BORDER-LEFT:#0000ff 2px solid;\">\n    <div class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927OutlookMessageHeader\" dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"\n size=\"2\">-----Original Message-----<br><b>From:</b> Erik Husby \n    [mailto:ehusby@...]<br><b>Sent:</b> Wednesday, November 28, \n    2001 10:50 AM<br><b>To:</b> &#39;junit@yahoogroups.com&#39;<br><b>Subject:</b> RE: \n    [junit] Capturing the standard out of a program that I&#39;m \n    testing<br><br></font></div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\" size=\"2\">I \n    believe that what you want to do is to redefine System.out. That can be done \n    by:</font></span></div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\"></font></span>&nbsp;</div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\">System.setOut( new PrintStream(...));</font></span></div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\"></font></span>&nbsp;</div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\">Your PrintStream could be a ByteArrayOutputStream if you want to \n    capture the data to memory.</font></span></div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\"><font face=\"Arial\" color=\"#0000ff\"\n size=\"2\"></font></span>&nbsp;</div>\n    <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1683180927203574416-28112001\">\n    <p><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">M. Erik Husby</font> <br><font face=\"Arial\"\n size=\"2\">Phase Forward Corp</font> <br><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">1440 Main \n    St.</font> <br><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Waltham, MA&nbsp; 02451-1623</font> \n    <br><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\">Office: 781.902.4559</font> <br><font face=\"Arial\"\n size=\"2\">Mobile: 781.354.6669</font> <br><font face=\"Arial\"\n size=\"2\">erik.husby@...</font> </p></span></div><br><br><tt>To \n    unsubscribe from this group, send an email \n    to:<br>junit-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.com<br></tt><br><br><tt>Your use of \n    Yahoo! Groups is subject to the <a rel=\"nofollow\"\n target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://docs.yahoo.com/info/terms/\">Yahoo! Terms of Service</a>.</tt> \n    <br></blockquote><br><br><tt>To \n  unsubscribe from this group, send an email \n  to:<br>junit-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.com<br></tt><br><br><tt>Your use of \n  Yahoo! Groups is subject to the <a rel=\"nofollow\"\n target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://docs.yahoo.com/info/terms/\">Yahoo! Terms of Service</a>.</tt> \n<br></blockquote></span></blockquote></html> \n</div>", 
